title: Looking for a ranked team between Gold - Bronze
body:
Hey guys i am based in oceania and am currently looking for a ranked team. I can play every single role (Not picky) but my main is Mid lane. My current rank is Silver 4 and i am usually on everyday between 1hr - 4 hrs. I usually focus on Ap (Mage mid laners). I main leblanc, ahri, fizz, ori, annie, syndra and zed.
IGN = Zezpon
